'''山姆·歐德漢姆'''（{{lang-en|Sam Oldham}}；{{bd|1993年|2月17日}}）是一位[[英國|英國]][[競技體操|競技體操]]運動員<ref name="sponsorship">{{cite news|url=http://www.thisisnottingham.co.uk/news/Teenage-gymnast-course-gold-2012/article-568238-detail/article.html|title=Teenage gymnast on course for gold in 2012|author=Delia Monk|work=[[Nottingham_Post|Nottingham Post]]|date=24 December 2008|accessdate=10 October 2010|archive-date=2013-04-21|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130421121311/http://www.thisisnottingham.co.uk/news/Teenage-gymnast-course-gold-2012/article-568238-detail/article.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="nottspost">{{cite news|url=http://www.thisisnottingham.co.uk/news/won-gold-medal-broken-wrist/article-1781987-detail/article.html|title='I won gold medal with a broken wrist'|author=Jennifer Scott|work=[[Nottingham_Post|Nottingham Post]]|date=30 January 2010|accessdate=2 October 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101010030257/http://www.thisisnottingham.co.uk/news/won-gold-medal-broken-wrist/article-1781987-detail/article.html|archivedate=2010年10月10日}}</ref>，主要擅長單槓。2012年，他幫助英國獲得了[[2012年夏季奧林匹克運動會體操男子團體比賽|奧運會體操男子團體]]的銅牌。他也曾在2010年夏季青奧上摘得一枚金牌和一枚銀牌。

